item.title: CVE-2022-4681|2024-08-03T01:48:39.655Z -- unknown -- hide%20my%20wp
item.description: The Hide My WP WordPress plugin before 6.2.9 does not properly sanitize and escape a parameter before using it in a SQL statement via an AJAX action available to unauthenticated users, leading to a SQL injection.
